premise_source_doc_sentence: In addition to the 10 million dollar treaty purchase of the land rights from Panama , the United States paid to purchase the title to all the lands in the Canal Zone from the existing property owners including 40 million dollars paid to the French Canal Company for their properties and at least $ 4,728,889 paid to other private property owners .
